dct_title_s: Africa : corrected from observations of Mess. of ye Royal Societies at London and Paris
dct_description_sm: Decorative title cartouche depicting animals.; Dedication: To Owen Brigstocke of Lechdony in the County of Carmarthen.; Shows boundaries, rivers, forests and principal settlements, with tents symbolising areas inhabited by nomads, and notes.; Relief shown pictorially.; London meridian.
